1. *Ozbiljna* situacija je nastupila nakon što je vlada usvojila nove mere. (A serious situation arose after the government adopted the new measures.)

2. Velika *ozbiljnost* je prisutna u njegovim odlukama. (Great seriousness is present in his decisions.)

3. On je podneo *ozbiljne* primedbe na odluku. (He made serious objections to the decision.)

4. Ona je imala *ozbiljnih* zdravstvenih problema. (She had serious health problems.)

5. Ona je pokazala *ozbiljno* nepoštovanje prema njemu. (She showed serious disrespect towards him.)